<script type="application/json" data-for="htmlwidget-db4b96daa69d21a5a80d">{"x":{"filter":"none","vertical":false,"data":[["Communication and dissemintation of findings including public engagement","Communication and dissemintation of findings including public engagement","Communication and dissemintation of findings including public engagement"],["Creating a movie and using (social) media","Dissemination Meetings                   ","Creating Network                         "],["Getting involved with making a film documentary (2 community members and 3 participants), speaking to the media or providing information to the media (<5 community members and participants), getting involved in the World AIDS Day twitter event (1 community member and 1 participant)     ","PPI members took part in 4 dissemination activities, in collaboration with the investigators,  to disseminate I-Score Study research results in the HIV community. Also, the contribution of the PPI members to the research process was acknowledged and discussed in detail                  ","In addition to the benefits of sharing knowledge, skills, and resources, a final aspect of the dissemination phase of the research program was to create a community resource directory listing all service organizations, churches, and schools that might benefit from the research findings."],["<a href='https://tinyurl.com/Gafos2020'>Gafos 2020<\/a>        ","<a href='https://tinyurl.com/Lessard2019'>Lessard 2019<\/a>    ","<a href='https://tinyurl.com/Flaskerud1999'>Flaskerud 1999<\/a>"]],"container":"<table class=\"display\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Task<\/th>\n      <th>Strategy<\/th>\n      <th>Example for Strategy<\/th>\n      <th>Link<\/th>\n    <\/tr>\n  <\/thead>\n<\/table>","options":{"dom":"t","initComplete":"function(settings, json) {\n$(this.api().table().header()).css({'font-size': '13px'});\n$(this.api().table().body()).css({'font-size': '12px'});\n}","columnDefs":[{"name":"Task","targets":0},{"name":"St